  "text": "Recall that in Remark 6, we constructed simple examples where \u03be JL \u2248 1/2\u03ba and \u03b6 \u2248 1. One can check that the regularity parameter \u03c6 is a constant on these examples. In particular, the analysis presented in Jiang and Li [CITATION_1] implies a running time of\u00d5",
